text: Dario Vidošević (13 April 1968 - 27 May 2020) was a Croatian rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Croatian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Yugoslavia Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Split, Croatia Category:Coxswains (rowing)
